    <item>
      <title>对特朗普的痴迷给民主带来了代价</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/us/politics/trump-elections-politics.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统要求采取措施解决投票的公正性问题，他坚持对自己 2020 年选举的失败进行重新诉讼，同时想方设法对 2026 年的选举结果提出质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/17/us/politics/trump-elections-politics.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 04:34:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
